snippet.title: Monster Garden Trailer
snippet.description:
A monster friendship exploration RPG.

Coming Feb. 8th to Steam:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/719660/Monster_Garden/

and itch.io: https://wzackw.itch.io/monster-garden

Made by Zack Wood, with music by Darriell Butler and David Wells, and audio by Almut Schwacke
